<script>
const columns = [
  {
    title: '省',
    dataIndex: 'province_name'

  {

  },
  {
    title: '区',
    dataIndex: 'district_name'
  },
  {
    title: '门店',
    dataIndex: 'name'
  }
]
export default {
  name: 'SupportCourseShops',
  data() {
    return {
      columns,
      show: false,
      supportShopList: []
    }
  },
  props: {
    shopList: {
      type: Array,
      default: () => []

}
